      "type": "snippet",
      "title": "Bio (medium)",
      "content": "Vrijen Attawar is the founder of Careerspan and the builder of N5 OS—a file-first, portable, provenance-first operating system for founders. A non-technical founder actively learning to code, he focuses on trustworthy delegation, repeatable decision-making, and systems that preserve context.",
